  09 Feb 2003; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> :
  Added hppa to keywords.

*less-378-r2 (08 Feb 2003)

  08 Feb 2003; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> less-378-r2.ebuild :

  Change the LESS="-r" env variable to "-R".  This should close bug #13882.

*less-378-r1 (26 Dec 2002)

  26 Dec 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> less-378-r1.ebuild :

  Add /etc/env.d/70less containing 'LESS="-r"' for groff-1.18 and later support.

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
